item.title: PowerSuit seems to be missing
item.dc:creator: @Robb Rob B
item.description:
@Robb wrote:

Check the Mods list on the main menu to see if they appear. If they don’t, then try swapping profiles on the mod manager.

If they are loaded (in the list), then check the FAQ for why. If that still doesn’t work, please post again on here or this discord.
